## Theme Application

To apply the Ocean Breeze theme to a component, use the `.theme-1` class prefix:

```css
.theme-1 .component-name {
  /* Ocean Breeze theme styles */
}
```

Or apply theme variables directly:

```css
:root {
  --ocean-primary: #0066cc;
  --ocean-accent: #00a8e8;
  --ocean-light: #e6f3ff;
  --ocean-dark: #004080;
  --ocean-font: 'Inter', sans-serif;
}
```

## Accessibility

- Ensure sufficient color contrast (Primary Blue on white meets WCAG AA)
- Use focus states with visible outlines (box-shadow on inputs)
- Maintain readable font sizes (minimum 0.85rem for body text)
- Provide hover and active states for all interactive elements
